Dialogue: 0,0:36:29.52,0:36:30.74,Default,,0,0,0,,keyboard extension, it's quite
Dialogue: 0,0:36:30.74,0:36:31.13,Default,,0,0,0,,easy.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:31.32,0:36:32.31,Default,,0,0,0,,So, let's switch back over to
Dialogue: 0,0:36:32.31,0:36:33.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Xcode here and I'll show you how
Dialogue: 0,0:36:33.37,0:36:33.84,Default,,0,0,0,,to do that.
