Dialogue: 0,0:37:00.31,0:37:01.99,Default,,0,0,0,,For instance, it sets it up so
Dialogue: 0,0:37:01.99,0:37:02.73,Default,,0,0,0,,that this extension is
Dialogue: 0,0:37:02.73,0:37:04.11,Default,,0,0,0,,automatically embedded inside of
Dialogue: 0,0:37:04.11,0:37:04.75,Default,,0,0,0,,your app bundle.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:04.75,0:37:05.67,Default,,0,0,0,,So, you don't need to mess with
