Dialogue: 0,0:37:15.16,0:37:16.23,Default,,0,0,0,,use this because we already
Dialogue: 0,0:37:16.23,0:37:16.71,Default,,0,0,0,,wrote one.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:17.04,0:37:18.03,Default,,0,0,0,,So, I'm just going to tweak
