Dialogue: 0,0:38:27.66,0:38:30.19,Default,,0,0,0,,And there used to be -- now we
Dialogue: 0,0:38:30.19,0:38:31.82,Default,,0,0,0,,have to enable the custom
Dialogue: 0,0:38:31.82,0:38:33.43,Default,,0,0,0,,keyboard extension in the System
Dialogue: 0,0:38:33.43,0:38:34.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Settings, and there used to be a
