Dialogue: 0,0:38:35.93,0:38:36.26,Default,,0,0,0,,that.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:36.45,0:38:38.28,Default,,0,0,0,,But in new, in iOS 11, we
Dialogue: 0,0:38:38.28,0:38:39.59,Default,,0,0,0,,actually made it much simpler
Dialogue: 0,0:38:39.59,0:38:40.86,Default,,0,0,0,,for your users to enable your
Dialogue: 0,0:38:40.86,0:38:41.92,Default,,0,0,0,,custom keyboard extension.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:42.11,0:38:42.83,Default,,0,0,0,,So, I'm going to show you how
Dialogue: 0,0:38:42.83,0:38:43.62,Default,,0,0,0,,that works right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:43.62,0:38:46.09,Default,,0,0,0,,So, I'm going to go back to
Dialogue: 0,0:38:46.09,0:38:46.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Settings.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:48.43,0:38:50.17,Default,,0,0,0,,So, all you need to do, to
Dialogue: 0,0:38:50.17,0:38:51.83,Default,,0,0,0,,enable your -- to allow your
